title: Taggart Episodes 34-41
description:
This is the 1st third of a set of Hard to Find Taggart Episodes between Mark McManus and Alex Norton. Since there are several differences on the internet as to which season the episodes fall into...........I shall number them as episodes aired from the start of TAGGART and not use the season they fell into.

E34 Devils Advocate 

E35 Angel Eyes

E36 Dead Mans Chest

E37 Apocalypse

E38 Babushka

E39 Berserker 

E40 Out of Bounds 

E41 Dead Reckoning
